title: 795. Deep Dive on Tyreek Hill's Trade to the Dolphins
itunes:title: 795. Deep Dive on Tyreek Hill's Trade to the Dolphins
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Rhett Lewis are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special podcast, the guys do a deep dive on wide receiver Tyreek Hill being traded from the Chiefs to the Dolphins. First, they look at the Chiefs and Jets' offers for Hill. Then, the pair focus on the Chiefs' perspective as they hit on why the team couldn't get a contract extension done and how the Chiefs could try to aim to replace Hill through the draft. After that, the duo discuss what the Jets could do in the draft after missing out on Hill. To wrap up the show, the guys talk about a special draft prospect and how teams value the safety position in the draft.

Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
